These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, kale, watermelon, lemon
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, pakistani, argentine, german
1. the pakistani is on the left of the polish##1
2. the person eating radish is the german##1
3. the argentine is on the right of the polish##1
4. the person eating kale is on the left of the german##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lemon | watermelon | kale | radish   |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | polish     | argentine   | german |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, chess, traveling, reading
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, weightlifting, golf, skiing
1. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | reading | chess | dancing    |
| Sport   | golf    | weightlifting      | basketball | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, hiking, magic-tricks
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, scientific, documentary, musical
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | board-games | magic-tricks | hiking   | card-games |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | documentary | musical | scientific         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, zombie, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, ice-hockey, rowing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | epic | animation  | zombie      |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | soccer   | rowing | swimming |

