.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, broccoli, peas, pear
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, ferret, goat, snake
1. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person eating peas##1
3. the person eating pear is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pear | peas | broccoli | grapefruit |
| Pet    | goldfish       | snake | goat | ferret     |

