.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: british, indonesian, spanish, turkish
4 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, turtle, pony
1. the indonesian is on the far right##1
2. the turkish is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the spanish##1
5. the owner of the pony is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | turkish | spanish | british | indonesian |
| Pet           | bird      | turtle | pony | guinea-pig    |

