2. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
3. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
5. the fan of country is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | trance | country | metal | d&b  |
| Pet           | hamster | pony | rabbit       | lizard |

