.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, videographer, accountant, dressmaker
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, motorbike, helicopter, bike
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the videographer##1
2. the person driving the bike is the dressmaker##1
3. the videographer is on the right of the journalist##1
4. the accountant is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | accountant | journalist      | videographer | dressmaker |
| Transport   | subway          | motorbike | helicopter     | bike    |

