2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
5. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster    | time-travel       | thriller | sports   |
| Transport     | bike | tram | boat   | subway |

