.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, soy-milk, iced-tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, motorbike, boat
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | mirinda | soy-milk  | almond-milk | iced-tea |
| Transport   | boat | motorbike | bike          | airplane    |

