.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, tea, 7up, cola
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, country, jazz, indie
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of punk##1
2. the fan of indie is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking tea is the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | 7up | tea  | lemonade | cola |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | jazz | indie           | country   |

