2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping | dancing | collecting | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | horror     | mystery    | thriller      | satire   |

