.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, german, malaysian, colombian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, airplane, ship
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the german##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the colombian##1
3. the dutch is on the left of the malaysian##1
4. the colombian is the person driving the ship##1
5. the person driving the bus is on the left of the german##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | dutch | malaysian | german | colombian   |
| Transport     | airplane  | bus    | helicopter       | ship |

 